OL,7,FVictims of the Post Office scandal who
OL,8,Fare seeking compensation have one
OL,9,Fmonth to go before the application
OL,10,Fdeadline for a key redress scheme.
OL,12,FCurrent and former postmasters are
OL,13,Fbeing urged to apply to the Horizon
OL,14,FShortfall Scheme (HSS) before the
OL,15,Fclosing date of January 31.
