OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FHSS was set up in 2020 for those who
OL,8,Fexperienced shortfalls in their
OL,9,Faccounts due to the Horizon system but
OL,10,Fwere not wrongfully convicted or part
OL,11,Fof the group of claimants who took the
OL,12,FPost Office to the High Court.
OL,14,FIt is one of several redress schemes
OL,15,Fset up to compensate postmasters who
OL,16,Fwere affected by previous faulty
OL,17,Fversions of the computer system, which
OL,18,Fmade it look like money was missing
OL,19,Ffrom their branch accounts.
