OL,4,Capply to key Horizon compensation
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FHSS claimants can choose between a
OL,8,F#75,000 fixed sum offer or a full
OL,9,Fassessment of their case if they
OL,10,Fbelieve they are entitled to more.
OL,12,FSome #769 million has been paid out
OL,13,Fthrough the scheme, as of November 28,
OL,14,Faccording to the Post Office.
OL,16,FIt accounts for more than half the
OL,17,Ftotal #1.33 billion worth of financial
OL,18,Fredress to more than 10,000 Horizon IT
OL,19,Fvictims across all schemes.
