OL,4,Capply to key Horizon compensation
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FNeil Brocklehurst, chief executive of
OL,8,Fthe Post Office, said: "I want
OL,9,Feveryone affected by the Horizon IT
OL,10,Fscandal who is eligible for financial
OL,11,Fredress to receive it as soon as
OL,12,Fpossible.
OL,14,F"There is just one month left to apply
OL,15,Fto the Horizon Shortfall Scheme, so
OL,16,Fplease don't wait ` applications must
OL,17,Fbe received by January 31.
OL,19,F"If you have questions, our team is
OL,20,Fready to talk through your options
OL,21,Fwith you.
