OL,7,F"Postmaster representative groups,
OL,8,Fsuch as the National Federation of Sub-
OL,9,FPostmasters, Voice of the Postmaster,
OL,10,For the Communication Workers Union,
OL,11,Fcan also offer support."
OL,13,FThe long-running battle for justice
OL,14,Faccelerated dramatically after ITV
OL,15,Fbroadcast the drama Mr Bates Vs The
OL,16,FPost Office, which highlighted the
OL,17,Fscandal.
OL,19,FIt marks two years since the drama was
OL,20,Faired on New Years Day 2024.
