OL,7,FPost Office minister Blair McDougall
OL,8,Fsaid: "It is my priority that
OL,9,Fpostmasters receive fair redress as
OL,10,Fquickly as possible in recognition of
OL,11,Fthe hurt that so many of them and
OL,12,Ftheir families suffered.
OL,14,F"The Horizon Shortfall Scheme has been
OL,15,Fcentral to this effort, paying out
OL,16,Fover #700 million to more than 6,000
OL,17,Fpeople affected.
